skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chikka magazine
des:
Chikka Magazine is a skill that will help you find out about important community announcements and upcoming events in the Filipino community in addition to other Asian communities in Arizona. 

This skill also users to listen to recent podcasts and audio articles. Also available is access to our radio station which features targeted programming along with easy listening music for relaxation and work. 

Say "Help" to hear available commands.

You can say:

"Alexa, open Chikka Magazine"
"Alexa, start Chikka Magazine"
"Alexa, launch Chikka Magazine"

Please leave a 5-star review if you love this skill, or send us an email with your suggestions at contribute@chikkamagazine.com. Your 5-star reviews encourage us to keep making more great skills, thanks!
